{"tid":1098208,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【醫院辱華？】LED屏幕打出「日本萬歲」 警拘31歲男子","createTime":"2019-04-09T02:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T02:01:46.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"583f39975883729c4cf6c3a9e1a43e2afd1d26fb","tid":1098208,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T02:01:46.000Z","msg":"河北保定高陽縣醫院的LED顯示屏上，今日出現辱華字句。當地警方通報指，下午3時許已拘捕一名31歲李姓男子，目前案件有待調查。<br />\n<br />\n醫院的LED屏幕上，顯示「日本萬歲」、「支持中國的是傻X」、「打到（倒）中國的帝國主義」等字眼。有網民發現後拍攝短片，遭到醫院保安阻止。院方其後切斷屏幕電源，並聯同高陽縣衞生局就事件報警。內地記者多次撥打高陽縣醫院的電話，但均無人接聽回應事件。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190408/59464901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190408%2F59464901&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLZHrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=7a0e318a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190408%2F59464901&h=016502ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190408/59464901</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kUaT47A3WU4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkUaT47A3WU4&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLZHrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=54ce8be7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kUaT47A3WU4</a>"}]}